summary: An external email from 'aMMIla' to an FBI contact in New York, sent on March 3, 2021, with the subject line referencing pictures and containing an attached image file named 'IMG_2687.jpg' that appears to show a Bentley vehicle's license plate in a driveway.

persons.name: aMMIla
persons.context: Appears as the sender of an email to an FBI contact, providing a photo of a Bentley license plate in a driveway.

events.title: Email with Bentley photo sent to FBI
events.description: An email with the subject '[EXTERNAL EMAIL] - Pics' was sent from 'aMMIla' to an FBI contact in New York, containing an attached image file named 'IMG_2687.jpg' that shows a Bentley license plate in a driveway.

keyFacts: An email was sent to the FBI in New York on March 3, 2021, with the subject referencing pictures.
The email contained an attached image file named 'IMG_2687.jpg' that appears to show a Bentley vehicle's license plate in a driveway.
The email was sent from an individual or entity identified as 'aMMIla'.
The email is marked as external, indicating it originated from outside the FBI's internal network.
